<p>reckon as if they could not give them a day off, they might just as well for the men will learn nothing &amp; it will do them a lot of harm perhaps, just imagine yourself carrying about 30 lbs on your back &amp; careering over the snow, with hands like ice &amp; the snow falling thick, then when they come home, they have only cold &amp; crowded tents to go into, its enough to make a man jump up &amp; never come down again. So much for the military life, no wonder a big &percnt; of the men are crook, &amp; then they wonder why the men don't turn out smartly,  to make sure I would not go on parade this morning I fixed my boot up with the aid of a friendly bayonet, for they are quite beyond repair. <br/>I believe we are moving from here</p>
